title: China's old space lab burns up over the Pacific Ocean
text:
China's old space lab burns up over the Pacific Ocean 10:10am BST - 01:16 
China's space authority says the Tiangong-1 space station re-entered the Earth's atmosphere and burned up over the South Pacific. Anita Li reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
